# Configuration for the release-tooling tasks. Copy this file to .env
# (gitignored) in this directory and fill in the values — each task loads it
# automatically, wherever it is invoked from. Variables set in the real
# environment take precedence over .env.
#
# Per-run parameters (PREVIOUS, CURRENT, TAG, DATE_START, DATE_END) do NOT
# belong here — pass them on the command line.

# GitHub personal access token; `repo` rights are needed for contributor-stats.
# https://docs.github.com/en/authentication/keeping-your-account-and-data-secure/creating-a-personal-access-token
#GITHUB_TOKEN=
